(firstQuint)Trans-perineal Repair With or Without Limited Internal Sphincterotomy for Treatment of Type I Anterior Rectocele.

 Transperineal repair of anterior rectocele is performed in two groups of patients, the first will undergo limited posterior internal sphincterotomy, the second group will not have internal sphincteroromy.

 The two groups are compared regarding recurrence of rectocele and improvement of symptoms.

